<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Cancellation Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #d9534f;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0.5em 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Dear <%= userName %>,</h1>
    <p>We regret to inform you that the event you booked tickets for, <strong><%= eventName %></strong>, scheduled at <%= eventVenue %> on <%= eventTime %>, has been canceled by the organizer.</p>
    <p>Booking ID: <%= bookingId %></p>
    <p>Number of tickets: <%= ticketCount %></p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free to contact our support team.</p>
    <p>We apologize for the inconvenience and hope to see you at one of our other events soon.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>Event Team</p>
</body>
</html>
